ZH: 我每天都会花时间念书。
EN: I spend time reading books every day.

ZH: 我念书到深夜才罢休。
EN: I study late into the night before stopping.

ZH: 她在图书馆里静静地念书。
EN: She quietly reads in the library.

ZH: 他懒惰不爱念书。
EN: He is lazy and doesn't like to study.

ZH: 孩子们念书要专心。
EN: Children need to concentrate when studying.

ZH: 这本书很适合初学者念书。
EN: This book is suitable for beginners to study.

ZH: 妈妈总是鼓励我多念书。
EN: Mom always encourages me to study more.

